deo/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2922760/extras/42f12eb6072ce2b921c78b2a54768889.mp4?t=1715446786\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>不要踩到黑色涂痕，不要被倒吊的人追上。当你通过一个又一个的房间后，你就赢了。</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2922760/extras/b2c279b77af230826ae4e82b26548208.poster.avif?t=1715446786\" width=500 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2922760/extras/b2c279b77af230826ae4e82b26548208.webm?t=1715446786\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2922760/extras/b2c279b77af230826ae4e82b26548208.mp4?t=1715446786\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><i>靠你的记忆，果敢，策略，运气活着离开这座充满不可见危险物的“捏鼠妙妙屋”吧。</i><br><br>这款游戏是我在制作常规解密恐怖游戏中，构思出的一种新型怪物追逐战。<br>游戏虽然是以躲避怪物为核心，但不会出现跳脸杀等恐怖画面，可以放心游玩。<br>游戏的总体流程不长，但挑战难度很高。本质上是一种新玩法的实验性小游戏.",
